column1:
Notes:
Data are presented in '000s
:  represents data that are unavailable.
. represents calculated unit costs where either data are zero or a component part is not available. 
2013-14 Bridging Year data has been sourced from the PSS-EX1 return for that year and then calculated by the HSCIC to allow for comparable data between 2014-15 and the previous year.
Numerator data are Gross Total expenditure associated with Council-funded support in Financial Year
Denominator data are number of care weeks associated with Council-funded support in Financial Year
. represents calculated unit costs where data are either zero or where component part/s  are not available.
Unit costs for England and regions have been based on data from councils where both the numerator and denominator are available and not zero.

Unit Costs were reported in previous years it should be noted that they are not comparable due to a change in activity reporting in this years return. For more details please consult the guidance document http://www.hscic.gov.uk/socialcarecollections2015
Please note: Data quality issues affecting primary support reasons have been reported by some councils, see Appendix B in the report for this publication for further information.
